-12-26 11:05:22'),(3264,108,'FjKNBtlK24UKFDELuU_fNkBnHr_6','(BUMP!) And then something went BUMP!\nHow that bump made us jump!','FkA_aF0icf3qWyyRzzGAMyq0E51F',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3265,108,'Fn4ca9CtOAvjhA5HCGFZT_6Xsy1z','We looked! Then we saw him step in on the mat!\nWe looked! And we saw him!\nThe Cat in the Hat!\nAnd he said to us, “Why do you sit there like that?”\n“I know it is wet and the sun is not sunny.\nBut we can have lots of good fun that is funny!”','FkBLsN0QWn8Moisg6GWtet5uK-K_',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3266,108,'Fpq9ULQAqAZSazJ6PmsczhMJO3Ou','“I know some good games we could play,” said the cat.\n“I know some new tricks,” said the Cat in the Hat.\n“A lot of good tricks. I will show them to you.\nYour mother will not mind at all if I do.”\nThen Sally and I did not know what to say.\nOur mother was out of the house for the day.','Fm6RGAdA6to9t6q9MP3kmwnRXH8Z',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3267,108,'FlSmBjJFvHChkK3FOLtHJusVObV6','But our fish said, “No! No! Make that cat go away!\nTell that Cat in the Hat you do NOT want to play.\nHe should not be here. He should not be about.\nHe should not be here when your mother is out!”','FtYJUcNjevVlm4Sark5gNZBAWPbU',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3268,108,'FprOGO1asIZavlcjEJsD-4k9I55I','“Now! Now! Have no fear. Have no fear!” said the Cat .\n\"My tricks are not bad,\"Said the Cat in the Hat.\n“Why, we can have lots of good fun, if you wish, with a game that I call UP-UP-UP with a fish!”\n“Put me down!” said the fish. “This is no fun at all!\nPut me down!” said the fish. “I do NOT wish to fall!”','FuFhihlBepcLBZIiIbH52fLQ-MG7',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3269,108,'FtLkvtaWYjOyrCn-jyse6zW27lfw','“Have no fear!” said the cat. “I will not let you fall.\nI will hold you up high as I stand on a ball.\nWith a book on one hand! And a cup on my hat!\nBut that is not ALL I can do!” said the cat...','Fu2dpCRvkIaNNVB0raDwOTlV99d7',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3270,108,'FjNuu-KOlJ--6LLAMBT6x1to-ROV','“Look at me! Look at me now!” said the cat.\n“With a cup and a cake on the top of my hat!\nI can hold up TWO books! I can hold up the fish!\nAnd a little toy ship!\nAnd some milk on a dish! And look!\nI can hop up and down on the ball!\nBut that is not all!\nOh, no. That is not all...','FgaoRdZJXeju1hcx1V4TVxmDgoU2',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:22','2017-12-26 11:05:22'),(3271,107,'FtLBAinkYXi7N7vNZmkVBAjAD1-Q','“Look at me! Look at me! Look at me NOW!\nIt is fun to have fun but you have to know how.\nI can hold up the cup and the milk and the cake!\nI can hold up these books! And the fish on a rake!\nI can hold the toy ship and a little toy man!\nAnd look! With my tail I can hold a red fan!\nI can fan with the fan as I hop on the ball!\nBut that is not all.\nOh, no. That is not all...”','FvG60bNE6p1YiAzPBkH5dC7Wt2IM',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3272,107,'FlTz6HR6LdLhXLDPMpyNPebHaj8m','That is what the cat said...then he fell on his head!\nHe came down with a bump from up there on the ball.\nAnd Sally and I, we saw ALL the things fall!','Fq7r1BbFjGwrX-2jxxlUMxj56CNu',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3273,107,'FvqPD6XvU8wp1-68z2JhLCkQbJWP','And our fish came down, too. He fell into a pot!\nHe said, “Do I like this? Oh, no! I do not.\nThis is not a good game,” said our fish as he lit.\n“No, I do not like it, not one little bit!”','Fq3VQ7E4ZvzOm3JFgyM9OMt-enBl',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3274,107,'FsLsp7Rr3LmU5qCtsWlBP8kRi7Ce','“Now look what you did!” said the fish to the cat.\n“Now look at this house!\nLook at this! Look at that!\nYou sank our toy ship, sank it deep in the cake.\nYou shook up our house and you bent our new rake.\nYou SHOULD NOT be here when our mother is not.\nYou get out of this house!” said the fish in the pot.','FrjeBaXneh4zi3WstepNnAL1pYjY',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3275,107,'Fu5RmmGeKJINnQWiB7LofGRbByLm','“But I like to be here. On, I like it a lot!”\nSaid the Cat in the Hat to the fish in the pot.\n“I will NOT go away. I do NOT wish to go!\nAnd so,” said the Cat in the Hat,\n“So, so, so...\nI will show you another good game that I know!”','FiWUC8GOUugolHKU_zbjuQ1tYNO_',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3276,107,'FmpYtOb1zAgS_UIEclB_Z08IjTLg','And then he ran out.\nAnd, then, fast as a fox\nthe Cat in the Hat came back in with a box.\nA big red wood box. It was shut with a hook.\n“Now look at this trick,” said the cat. “Take a look!”','Fj77yFIsiIIqTT-mduTKGY9S7kKP',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3277,107,'FmshuF21GEMyESQAr2z0AjHx-SGk','Then he got up on top with a tip of his hat.\n“I call this game FUN-IN-A-BOX,” said the cat.\n“In this box are two things I will show to you now.\nYou will like these two things,” said the cat with a bow.','FsR1nwyRb-6qeZK4wk7QA1GFKS4k',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3278,107,'FuVtBEOxqbr1vF1HbgcMLjYYYGaW','“I will pick up the hook.\nYou will see something new. Two things.\nAnd I call them Thing One and Thing Two.\nThese Things will not bite you.\nThey want to have fun.”\nThen, out of the box came Thing Two and Thing One!\nAnd they ran to us fast.\nThey said, “How do you do?\nWould you like to shake hands with Thing One and Thing Two?”','Fv8BYFuTmk1SW3ZY65-vk6y6C50j',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3279,107,'FjAqFHN35ZZpkXyvS3G7-ZeDOPV2','And Sally and I did not know what to do.\nSo we had to shake hands with Thing One and Thing Two.\nWe shook their two hands.But our fish said,\n“No! No! These Things should not be in this house! Make them go!\nThey should not be here when your mother is not!\nPut them out! Put them out!” said the fish in the pot.','Fmzz6AXm3T6gPyXnMm3GSKC2kUdL',0,'2017-12-26 11:05:48','2017-12-26 11:05:48'),(3280,107,'Fn-cL9ECDtJdiGyHRn3yJeq4oRkI','“Have no fear, little fish,” said the Cat in the Hat.\n“These Things are good Things