KPiqjGRUqygML','Long Vowel Combination:\nee - green\nVowel Combination:\noo - snoozed \nBlend:\nqu - queen','FsJwoXSpWXO9V3jU5Y9Lz4hkU8KN',0,'2018-02-09 03:48:19','2018-02-09 03:48:19'),(4884,190,'FhYpxUfjWPVx0v_Yvb9U2vLDTuRg','The Berenstain Bears and the Baby Chipmunk\n--by Stan & Jan Berenstain','Ft1gOrCgcWoaC7-wwOUZorICJ9_T',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4885,190,'FlExyRVpN2hdn0gWJ2JPscqMQ9Gw','It was a lovely day in Bear Country.\nThe Bear family was enjoying the sunshine.\nPapa was resting.\nMama was working in the garden.\nHoney Bear was watching Mama.\nBrother and Sister were playing catch.','FnY2mH9iGIhOYrMOxvPmpz6QFiiP',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4886,190,'FpScoZLbrxbOyk60zV6R4ceJcGJC','“Look!” said Sister. “A mouse!”\n“That is not a mouse,” said Brother.\n“If it is not a mouse, what is it?” asked Sister.\n“It is a chipmunk,” said Mama.\n“A baby chipmunk.”','FnBYKJmwT52UX3pujh7Q7pHAd8ey',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4887,190,'Fhfs7lGTIjo55glwuoO0pcNkSiPJ','“May we keep him, Mama?” cried Sister.\n“May we? May we?”\n“Look,” said Brother.\n“His eyes are not open yet.”\n“That’s right,” said Mama.\n“This baby should be with his mother.\nBut she will not come if she sees us.\nCome. We will hide behind the tree house.\nMaybe she will come.”','FmaahOGsHWrm0xnjUWqJ9jEXrG10',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4888,190,'FrzpVV38K3qkwx127Tt6YAOg4HZ8','The Bears watched and watched.\nBut the mother chipmunk did not come.\n“Now may we keep him?” cried Sister.\n“May we? May we?” \n“I think we shall have to,” said Mama.\n“At least for a while.”\n“That is right,” said Papa.\n“Babies need to be fed and kept warm.”','FphUDyEBy01SC5XJ9THmZu_9A9hE',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4889,190,'Fq_gELdNHLkjRfIWzzB5EIbXfZVu','“Papa, do you have a clean hanky?” asked Mama.\nMama picked up the baby chipmunk and tucked him into Papa’s hanky.\nThen they took the baby chipmunk into the house.','FtZBQF6ur2KVYbtqZ3FOxx_LXfi5',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4890,190,'FszKxYGVZY20p050wVI_pvVVsFXa','“Sister,” said Mama.\n“Please get one of your doll’s baby bottles.\nBrother, please get some milk and honey.”\nThe baby chipmunk was very hungry.\nAs he drank from the bottle, he opened his eyes.\nThey were big and brown.\n“Let’s named him Brown Eyes,” said Sister.\n“That is as good a name as any,” said Mama.','Fn3uwbn1xAjb_877mQXZivTOzGGv',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4891,190,'FmEYg99srKZK-Gs5rj4dVT5zGTaZ','Papa got a box for a bed.\nBrother made it cozy.\nBrown Eyes liked his new bed.\nBaby Honey liked to watch him.\nSoon Brown Eyes was fast asleep.','Fv6GvrwBgSxWIzMo35ijxnuv4srE',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4892,190,'FmTaeS_jHSPN5KAkmSWcLPJ7Z_d7','The next morning, Sister and Brother woke up early.\nThey ran downstairs to see Brown Eyes.\nThe box was there.\nBut he was not.\nThey look all around.\n“There he is!” said Brother.\nBrown Eyes was up on the table.\nHe had knocked over the sugar bowl.\nHe was eating sugar.\n“I guess he needs more than milk and honey,” said Sister.','FoeLGIZ0f-V4fuaKlIVZYVbgNFuB',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4893,190,'FlqIN1qxbnmaBUbSWyTxkRjQEdcn','The cubs went outside.\nThey got some seeds.\nBrown Eyes was very small.\nBut he had big, chipmunk teeth.\nJust like that, the seeds were gone.\nBrown Eyes loved to play.\nWhat he loved to do most was explore.\nHe explored Mama’s vegetable bin.\nHe explored Papa’s desk.','Flt_Vhtaf2D4JRQOci-DOXYp0ozX',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4894,190,'FmlmI-wMY5lONkGfquYoELfSU_qE','He explored Mama’s sewing basket.\nThen one day, he explored one place too many.\nHe explored Papa’s pant leg-\nall the way up to the knee!\nWhile he was up there, he tried out his big, sharp teeth.\nYIPE! YOW!','FhXQ917anlLNMAKTerrAfNZh6QD7',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4895,190,'Fqygx13caNKqimtvY8o3K6ysN8Kz','“You know what I think?” asked Mama.\n“I think Brown Eyes is telling us something.\nHe is telling us he is ready to go out in the world.\nHe is ready to join his friends.”\n“But, Mama!” said Sister.\n“I don’t want him to go! I love him so!”','FoQvvqWH_pueaogEVixATdo2PFnz',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4896,190,'FsF06rAabnHyUl-6J7GXq3mC7ogP','“We all love him,” said Mama.\n“But it is not fair to make him a pet.\nChipmunks need to be free.\nThey need to explore.”','FhKbAbp5IzS_qe7gOOZhcvG_kLWj',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4897,190,'FuwAfmVQMyrK-LPmJWidDr5DjiUs','“There are not many good places to explore inside.”\nThe cubs thought about: Mama’s vegetable bin,\nPapa’s desk, \nMama’s sewing basket,\nand Papa’s pant leg.','FvpfWDvtfD0Mq96MNK5X7M9FER7a',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4898,190,'FheJ0Fsu2Njg8W11jBOJeZOZBcqo','“Outside,” said Mama, \n“Brown Eyes will be able to explore all of nature.”\nAs usual, Mama was right.\nThe Bear family didn’t even have to say good-bye.','Fg9RxWs5rIz_d5QiigEi-DCJpck3',0,'2018-02-11 03:36:18','2018-02-11 03:36:18'),(4899,191,'Fj1H0Kz7LtXIg_uKRbPbTRK2lt-O','The Berenstian Bears Clean House\n--by Stan & Jan Berenstain','Fgo9HGUm6k-JJK5v2yGG9uqidX-A',0,'2018-02-11 03:49:45','2018-02-11 03:49:45'),(4900,191,'Fouuf9fXFglUTSPR79AJ7JbhvizE','“It is spring,” said Mama Bear.\n“It is time to clean our house.”\n“I will help,” said Papa.\n“I will help,” said Brother.\n“I will help,” said Sister.','Flhl7OIapnbXIxTOxJZRJLei5SJi',0,'2018-02-11 03:49:45','2018-02-11 03:49:45'),(4901,191,'FhsN-y04hu9pGTnTymQDH6LpT7Mf','“Good,” said Mama.\n“We will clean our house from the top to the bottom,\nfrom the bottom to the top.”\nThey started at the bottom.','Fhgw7KDxl0DG_qStydfRKVbiO_Vw',0,'2018-02-11 03:49:45','2018-02-11 03:49:45'),(4902,191,'FqwNIwHaKhTxpq3G-mMrLIbUKezM','“My goodness,” said Mama.\n“There are too many things.\nIt is hard to clean with so many things.”\n“We will have a yard sale,” said Papa.\n“We 