7VdHGJhWBNZf','“You know something?” said Papa.\n“Digging for treasure is hot work!”\n“Ha! Ha! Ha!” cried the laughing gulls.\n“Hmm,” said Papa.\n“Do you think those gulls are laughing at us and our treasure hunt?”','FqWECtJyMRq5ojqNMYvZd8L9K2cs',0,'2018-02-27 05:43:10','2018-02-27 05:43:10'),(6339,222,'FmaweYQivbbr_WCUMczp8ihT02G2','“No way!” said Brother.\n“We came looking for treasure and we found it.\nWe found the treasure of the sea!”\n“That’s right,” said Sister.\n“A whole bucket full!”','FrcVluEOO-UAJdY1n2TCHHiBksqK',0,'2018-02-27 05:43:10','2018-02-27 05:43:10'),(6340,222,'FjkypDRnkNMtnb6R39l1QnJyGzJa','“Time for a dip!” said Papa.\nAfter they cooled off they headed back to the house to show Mama their treasure.','FsR8lvmkTbBwld-hR1Mg2fhSHF3H',0,'2018-02-27 05:43:10','2018-02-27 05:43:10'),(6341,222,'Fg_o_RdnW06s4IYes8Sq5I91R5II','“Papa,” said Brother,\n“What are you going to do with the treasure map?“\n“Hmm,” said Papa, \n“I may just leave it in the closet for the next papa bear.”','Fpv6QDdEbmtd0Tvpc2UEoLx2Buzb',0,'2018-02-27 05:43:10','2018-02-27 05:43:10'),(6342,221,'FkKfgw8yE5biPfvkiTArIXLU6nUj','The Berenstain Bears’ New Pup\n--by Stan & Jan Berenstain\n故事梗概\n有一天，Berenstain熊妈妈带着两个熊宝宝去农民Ben那里买新鲜的鸡蛋。农民Ben的小狗Queenie生了狗宝宝。狗宝宝们好可爱、好活泼啊！熊宝宝们很想买一只回去。熊妈妈告诉熊宝宝，小狗可不是那么好养的，小狗需要有人照顾、有人跟着打扫卫生的。后来他们买了小狗吗？我们一起来揭晓吧！','FspdoYpatn705sCrZGCLkGN1yMkC',0,'2018-02-27 05:53:41','2018-02-27 05:53:41'),(6343,221,'Frk-oo99lBw-K5kL7fFTkJpKBpjV','One day Mama and the cubs went to Farmer Ben’s farm.\nThey went there to buy some fresh eggs.','FoCryGfr94hwA5DmK_rZeIxNzN6D',0,'2018-02-27 05:53:41','2018-02-27 05:53:41'),(6344,221,'FoZBPELmSMTj_paeB_llnb380D48','“Look!” said Brother. \n“There is a sign on Farmer Ben’s barn door.”\nThe sign said PUPS FOR SALE!\n“Hmm,” said Mama.\n“Farmer Ben’s dog, Queenie, must have had pups.”','Fr3dUNBPaa0CA4hX2ak_buyV18Xp',0,'2018-02-27 05:53:41','2018-02-27 05:53:41'),(6345,221,'FnJLkudnJzXrXdhgXzUnfSqCorqb','“Oh, Mama!” said Sister.\n“May we have o