Today George was curious about the big box on the man’s desk.','Fh_WUTymNU2UXft9abyhiqtS3mCq',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6775,143,'FtLQyCjWD-fyHh8j45y4ChxJRcUR','What could be in it?\nGeorge could not resist. He simply HAD to open it.\nIt was full of funny little pieces of all sorts of shapes and all sorts of colors.\nGeorge took one out. It looked like a piece of candy.\nMaybe it WAS candy. Maybe he could eat it.\nGeorge put the piece in his mouth -- and before he knew, he had swallowed it.','FvF8tfsxR1uQZlhdcUJZJ5iWo1jT',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6776,143,'FvcEGs4r7nBO5iioKYMXdWfZKlTL','A while later the man with the yellow hat came home.\n“Why, George,” he said,\n“I see you have already opened the box with the jigsaw puzzle.\nIt was supposed to be a surprise for you.\nWell, let’s go to work on it.”\nFinally the puzzle was finished\n-- well, almost finished.\nOne piece was missing.','Frtp-st18YMyZiIo81ckhw4g1mXQ',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6777,143,'FilPDfPWiJlidIi8a8nwqNOqKvMB','The man looked for it everywhere,\nbut he could not find it.\n“That’s strange,” he said, “It’s a brand-new puzzle.\nWell, it cannot be helped.\nMaybe we’ll find it in the morning.\nLet’s go to bed now, George.”\nThe next morning George did not feel well.\nHe had a tummy-ache and did not want to eat his breakfast.\nThe man was worried.\nHe went to the telephone and called Doctor Baker.\n“I’ll be over as soon as I can,” said the doctor.','FizZW2G54Uzd0IOTvgJ_GTlU3Jrz',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6778,143,'Fuh24Em8Hk4UOn9kpSb2hz2gSiCM','First Doctor Baker looked down George’s throat and felt his tummy.\nThen he took out his stethoscope and listened.\n“I’m not sure what’s wrong,” he said.\n“You’d better take George to the hospital\nand have an X-ray taken.\nI’ll call them and let them know you are coming.”\n“Don’t worry, George,” said the man when they were driving to the hospital,\n“you have been there before,\nwhen you broke you leg.\nRemember how nice the doctors and nurses were?”\nGeorge held his big rubber ball tight\nas they walked up the hospital steps.','Fqll24j8WZ6Db_gsXABrlrgsse3f',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6779,143,'FncbSNUpNCzwpb84FxvC9RmZ9PBp','A nurse took them down a long hallway to a room\nwhere she gave George something to drink that looked white and tasted sweet.\n“It is called barium,” the nurse explained.\n“It helps the doctors find out\nwhat is wrong with you, George.”\nIn the next room stood a big table, and a doctor was just putting on a heavy apron.\nThen he gave the man one just like it.\nGeorge was curious: Would he get one too?\nNo, he did not.\n“You get on that table, George,” the doctor said.\n“I am going to take some X-ray pictures of your insides.”\nHe pushed a button and there was a funny noise.\n“There-- now you may get up, and we will have the X-ray developed right away.”','FgPLK0Vii_4blGyKda1W-2M-kwS_',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6780,143,'FsdXdHbF8f3CsYBoOhukyZgUobLz','“Now let’s see... There is something there that should not be,”\nsaid the doctor when they were looking at the X-rays.\n“Why, that looks like...\nI think that must be the piece that was missing in our jigsaw puzzle yesterday!” said the man.\n“Well, well, well,” said the doctor,\n“at least we know now what is wrong with\nour little patient.\nI’ll tell Doctor Baker right away.\nGeorge will have to stay at the hospital\nfor a few days.\nThey’ll put a tube down his throat\nto get the piece out.\nIt’s only a small operation.\nI’ll call a nurse and have her take you\nto the admitting office.”\nMany people were waiting outside the office.\nGeorge had to wait too.\n“Look, Betsy,” the woman next to him\nsaid to her little girl,\n“there is Curious George!”\nBetsy looked up for a moment,\nbut she did not even smile.\nBetsy had never been to a hospital before.\nShe was scared.','FoqC8gQIAUnK1BahEZu_ex0o6O52',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6781,143,'FiObJc2uOMtyBC-14jt0xvMKOHa6','Finally it was George’s turn.\nA pretty young nurse took him to the next room --\nmy, how many rooms\nand how many nurses there were!\nOne nurse wrote down a lot of things about George:\nhis name and his address\nand what was wrong with him.\nAnother nurse put a bracelet around his wrist.\n“It has your name on it, George,” she said,\n“so that everybody knows who you are.”\nThen the pretty young nurse came back.\n“My name is Carol,” she said.\n“I am going to take you to your room now -- we call it the children’s ward -- and put you to bed. There will be lots of\nchildren to keep you company.”','Fg4ffKQxT_d162xpL_GtXU6Bbduc',0,'2018-03-08 01:31:37','2018-03-08 01:31:37'),(6807,250,'FpgeeCSEAHhd4OXCVby6atUWA5o_','Chickens\n--by Lynn Maslen Kertell\n','FhDv1ERRqM6LdI_ZfOBGLKvDTPg2',0,'2018-03-08 09:20:01','2018-03-08 09:20:01'),(6808,250,'Fg3kqCx7SxWHWoXb4w6hh0vQTOvh','Chicken Big and Chicken Little had two chairs, a big chair and a little chair.','Fpm5i0gYkcgXbdLNkmMKeS9-4JAN',0,'2018-03-08 09:20:01','2018-03-08 09:20:01'),(6809,250,'FmJP-8OWrd2DBKNziKnwCPMnJn7B','“Who will get the big chair?” said Chicken Little.\n“Who will get the little chair?” said Chicken Big.','FtVDabRW6P8RW4H2bkwyDn8bV1Ge',0,'2018-03-08 09:20:01','2018-03-08 09:20:01'),(6810,250,'FoT16MdrPs3nptrLaWLisrdrwkmQ','“Let us play a game,” they said.\n“One, two, three, GO!”\nChicken Big chased Chicken Little across the room.','Fl1Cw6bdRPZbMXfAHG82sfaMWg9K',0,'2018-03-08 09:20:01','2018-03-08 09:20:01'),(6811,250,'FgFZ-eTADKriVQr8iI3a0GqGQ5vI','Chicken Little sat in the big chair.\nChicken Big cheered and clapped her wings.','FmGuSOs8UjPNYwmPRSXUFkM3EvcP',0,'2018-03-08 09:20:01','2018-03-08 09:20:01'),(6812,250,'FqY3EpvaHGgESADVgVAFaVRaIJ-G','Chicken Little got up.\nShe chased Chicken Big.\nChicken Big sat in the little chair.','FiNi5TbCgBgorh_NuYwXPkoRBsYi',0,'2018-03-08 09:20:01','2018-03-08 09:20:01'),(6813,250,'FkEt5IyzwR2nAHZV6Jup952pBNMG','Chi