ike white stones,\nBut it’s too long to be stones!”said Tog.\n“Let’s keep digging and find out.”\nSaid Tig and Tog together.\n“你能看到那是什么吗？”Tig问，“这真的好大好怪啊”\n“看起来像白色的石头，但是比石头长好多”Tog说\n“我们一直挖就能知道是什么了”Tig和Tog一起说','Fj3da0FXZw4UEm_RrL4cfDK6xHnV',0,'2018-03-08 09:22:32','2018-03-08 09:22:32'),(6828,188,'FncmCVWQmrj22I84pyG0pyxV992e','After a lot of searching,\nTig and Tog found a wheelbarrow…\nWith the big shovel, Tig and Tog were able to dig deeper,\nand they could move more earth with the wheelbarrow.\nBut even the wheelbarrow and shovel were\'t enough!\nThey STILL needed something else to\ndig the thing out of the ground.\n找了很久之后，Tig和Tog发现了一辆独轮小推车\n有了大铁锹，Tig和Tog用能挖得更深一点\n她们用独轮车也能搬走更多的土\n但是即使是独轮车和铁锹也是不够的\n她们仍然需要别的东西把它挖出来','FiJh0YlXoFnYoobyMJHU_U9tQiYR',0,'2018-03-08 09:22:32','2018-03-08 09:22:32'),(6829,188,'FofOGZ7V-VEq92WwN7yP92DtnaxT','All day long Tig and Tog\nworked together, using all\nthe tools they had found.\nThey scratched, scooped, dug, tipped,\nand shoveled the earth around.\nBut even with all these\ntools and all their hard work.\nthey still needed something else\n to dig the thing out of the ground!\n一整天Tig和Tog都在一起工作，用了所有她们能找的工具\n她们刮啊，擦啊，挖啊，铲和倒土\n但即使是这样，她们还是需要别的东西去把它挖出来','FjKnWpwVK-FAXgs2H2PN4P8prnhs',0,'2018-03-08 09:22:32','2018-03-08 09:22:32'),(6830,188,'FjWY3HQYPC1xUmdQ8FSpjsEC5MgN','Suddenly, Tog had a very clever idea!\nLeaving Tig scratching her head,\nTog soon returned with a big yellow digger!\nWith three mighty shovels,\nthe digger cleared the earth!\nTig and Tog both looked on\nin amazement at what they had found…\n突然，Tog有一个绝妙的点子\n当Tig还在挠头的时候\nTog很快就开着一辆大的黄色的挖掘机回来了\n挖掘机用3个巨大的铁锹清除了土\nTig和Tog都很惊奇地看着她们发现的东西','FkDKUimAeZeLqkUWJcwt9JxZA0UT',0,'2018-03-08 09:22:32','2018-03-08 09:22:32'),(6831,188,'FuzvbDMBxQoJigu4xsu1r1X6AJnS','It was the most ENORMOUS dinosaur skeleton!\n那是一个非常大的恐龙的骨骼','FsLZMssNuCl6U7Nc_5m8tNxOCYCK',0,'2018-03-08 09:22:32','2018-03-08 09:22:32'),(6832,188,'Fh66NbT-LiXraoGAYu5MgrG-C0H7','And the stick？\nTig decided to share the stick